"add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Novo contato</"
"guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1853
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choosing this context menu option has exactly the same effect as clicking "
"the <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;New Contact&nbsp;</guibutton> button on the "
"Toolbar. See <link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-contact\">chapter 2 above</"
"link> for complete details."
msgstr ""
"Selecionar esta opção do menu de contexto tem exatamente o mesmo efeito que "
"clicar no botão <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;Novo contato&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"na barra de ferramentas. Consulte o <link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-contact"
"\">capítulo 2 acima</link>  para obter detalhes completos."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1859
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
